      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOWERING EARL (6) was in the placings last time but prior to that posted a fast 29.80 win over 520m at this track. Has the ability and looks hard to top. TARAWI BRUMBY (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 29.75 beating Super Sassy. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from eight starts. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. RUGGED ETHICS (2) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when third (31.94) at Maitland. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and seven minor placings. Will give a great sight again. TAKE A BREAK (5) hit the frame latest (30.03) when third at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has already won two times from this draw.",
